    Each employee has KPIs that are assigned to Metrics and derived from a master KPI

    New Metric created =>
        auto generate companyKPI details for all KPIs of type 'Company'.
        auto generate employeeKPI details for all active employees and assign 'Company' KPI or create empty KPI.
        auto generate employeeScores


